{"tid":1801143,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"黃/藍方面，牆頭草 犬儒 港豬 大愛撚邊類人最仆街？","createTime":"2019-12-28T11:53:01.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-28T11:59:33.000Z","uid":237096,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"02835a7dbdd329c244ebb04a7a6428f555d2f451","tid":1801143,"uid":237096,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-28T11:53:01.000Z","msg":"1.係黃絲面前撐黃絲，但係藍絲面前卻撐藍絲(牆頭草派）<br />\n<br />\n2.係黃絲面前罵黃絲，係藍絲面前罵藍絲，言語上兩邊各打五十大板(犬儒派)<br />\n<br />\n3.不聞不問，食玩訓 咩都唔想知咩都唔理(港豬派)<br />\n<br />\n4.同情兩邊，覺得兩邊都好慘(大愛撚)<br />\n<br />\n5.不分係黃定藍面前，一時又講d好黃嘅說話，一時又講d好藍嘅說話(精神分裂撚)"},{"pid":"e27e69bb80ef92a15a19d0c5f88430ffefd8f16d","tid":1801143,"uid":214192,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-28T11:57:52.000Z","msg":"大愛撚<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n其他嗰班係見風轉舵，邊邊贏面大就支持邊邊<br />\n係呢種情況同我講覺得黑警同手足一樣可憐？咁佢係手足比人打嘅時候用愛感化黑警囉"},{"pid":"98e3586ff41c2874a3051a45efbc5b37f60b9503","tid":1801143,"uid":258731,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-28T11:59:33.000Z","msg":"－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－<br />\n投票： <a href=\"https://forms.gle/hDfcr3wCsprrvnC37\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fforms.gle%2FhDfcr3wCsprrvnC37&d=9uLtkTaOKuy%2FgkD%2BHbzoNWt2mj8CN1oGBszRVJtr96Q%3D&h=e31b97ca\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://forms.gle/hDfcr3wCsprrvnC37</a><br />\n<br />\n【最後4日】全民票選十八區區議會主席與發言人－民主統戰部<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1800922\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1800922</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/phk5doO.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fphk5doO.jpg&h=40b71bc8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n投票： <a href=\"https://forms.gle/hDfcr3wCsprrvnC37\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fforms.gle%2FhDfcr3wCsprrvnC37&d=9uLtkTaOKuy%2FgkD%2BHbzoNWt2mj8CN1oGBszRVJtr96Q%3D&h=e31b97ca\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://forms.gle/hDfcr3wCsprrvnC37</a><br />\n快啲入黎